### SmartAid REST tests — Beneficiaries CRUD + search
### Note: search is allowed for admin AND shop_manager (mobile app lookup).
### Other endpoints are admin-only.

@host = http://localhost:3000

### Login as admin
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@smartaid.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Login as shop_manager (allowed to use search)
# @name loginManager
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "manager@smartaid.com",
  "password": "manager123"
}

### 1) GET /api/beneficiaries without token
# Expected: 401
GET {{host}}/api/beneficiaries

### 2) GET /api/beneficiaries as shop_manager
# Expected: 403 (list is admin only)
GET {{host}}/api/beneficiaries
Authorization: Bearer {{loginManager.response.body.token}}

### 3) GET /api/beneficiaries as admin (list all)
# Expected: 200
GET {{host}}/api/beneficiaries
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### 4) GET /api/beneficiaries/1
# Expected: 200
GET {{host}}/api/beneficiaries/1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### 5) GET /api/beneficiaries/9999
# Expected: 404
GET {{host}}/api/beneficiaries/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### 6) POST create beneficiary (qr_code auto-generated UUID)
# Expected: 201, qr_code is a UUID like "xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx"
# @name createBen
POST {{host}}/api/beneficiaries
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "REST Beneficiary",
  "phone_number": "+252699988888",
  "family_size": 4,
  "location": "Mogadishu - Wadajir",
  "profile_image_url": "https://example.com/photo.jpg"
}

### 7) POST missing phone_number
# Expected: 400
POST {{host}}/api/beneficiaries
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "No phone"
}

### 8) POST duplicate phone_number
# Expected: 409
POST {{host}}/api/beneficiaries
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dup",
  "phone_number": "+252611111111"
}

### 9) POST bad family_size
# Expected: 400
POST {{host}}/api/beneficiaries
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bad",
  "phone_number": "+252611200000",
  "family_size": -1
}

### 10) PUT partial update (location only)
# Expected: 200
PUT {{host}}/api/beneficiaries/{{createBen.response.body.beneficiary.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "location": "Mogadishu - Hodan"
}

### 11) PUT try to change qr_code — field is silently ignored
# Expected: 200, qr_code in response UNCHANGED from the original UUID
PUT {{host}}/api/beneficiaries/{{createBen.response.body.beneficiary.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "qr_code": "HACKED-QR-VALUE",
  "name": "REST Beneficiary v2"
}

### 12) PUT no fields
# Expected: 400
PUT {{host}}/api/beneficiaries/{{createBen.response.body.beneficiary.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 13) SEARCH by phone as admin
# Expected: 200, returns Fadumo Hassan
GET {{host}}/api/beneficiaries/search?phone=%2B252611111111
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### 14) SEARCH by phone as SHOP MANAGER (allowed!)
# Expected: 200
GET {{host}}/api/beneficiaries/search?phone=%2B252622222222
Authorization: Bearer {{loginManager.response.body.token}}

### 15) SEARCH by phone — unknown number
# Expected: 404
GET {{host}}/api/beneficiaries/search?phone=%2B252600000000
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### 16) SEARCH by qr_code (using QR captured from request #6)
# Expected: 200
GET {{host}}/api/beneficiaries/search?qr_code={{createBen.response.body.beneficiary.qr_code}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### 17) SEARCH with no query param
# Expected: 400 { "error": "Provide ?phone= or ?qr_code=" }
GET {{host}}/api/beneficiaries/search
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### 18) SEARCH with BOTH phone and qr_code
# Expected: 400 { "error": "Provide only one of ?phone= or ?qr_code=" }
GET {{host}}/api/beneficiaries/search?phone=x&qr_code=y
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
